lank">Ring bounty</a>. If you have the skills and desire to show that secur=
ity camera owners<em> could</em> control their footage=E2=80=94and want to =
collect $23,580=E2=80=94read on.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-h=
eight: 1.6em; color: #15212A;">Our bounty system, first and foremost, is ai=
med at drawing attention to what would be possible if we unlocked our techn=
ology. If we are successful in passing commonsense reforms to Sec. 1201 of =
the Digital Millennium Copyright Act, we can unleash innovation in the repa=
ir tool market and make our devices work for us.</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0=
 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6em; color: #15212A;">We believe that this kind of=
 outcome should be accessible to both the technically-inclined and the aver=
age consumer. That is why, in our original criteria, we specified that a wi=
nning solution could not modify the original hardware. As I told <a href=3D=
"https://fulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/ec5ad964?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f9=
8315f6032b" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decorati=
on: underline;" target=3D"_blank">WIRED</a>, =E2=80=9CThis needs to be a we=
ekend project where someone who was creeped out by a commercial and wants t=
o take back control can take care of it, get it done, and be able to sleep =
soundly at night knowing that they're the only ones who can see their foota=
ge.=E2=80=9D</p><p style=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6em; color:=
 #15212A;">In our effort to make it accessible, we made it too difficult to=
 solve. We have attempted to remedy that situation by updating the bounty c=
riteria. <strong style=3D"font-weight: 700;">Now, a winning solution can in=
volve the replacement or addition of up to two circuit-board components. </=
strong>We=E2=80=99ve kept the requirement that the modification process sho=
uld be carried out in one hour or less to strike the balance.</p><p style=
=3D"margin: 0 0 1.5em 0; line-height: 1.6em; color: #15212A;"><strong style=
=3D"font-weight: 700;">Tl;dr</strong> =E2=80=93 we want to pay out this bou=
nty, so we=E2=80=99ve made adjustments to make it possible. To submit your =
solution, double check that you=E2=80=99ve met all the <a href=3D"https://f=
ulu-foundation.ghost.io/r/867cf9fd?m=3Db503a08a-c4e6-4bfd-bc68-f98315f6032b=
" style=3D"overflow-wrap: anywhere; color: #1dfdc0; text-decoration: underl=
ine;" target=3D"_blank">criteria</a> and then contact the FULU bounty team =
at bounty@fulu.org.</p>
